    "result": {"pageContext":{"id":"/topic/Java并发工具包/底层原理/java内存模型/happens-before规则","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"happens-before规则"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在JSR-133规范中，提出了happens-before的概念，通过这个概念来阐述操作之间的内存可见性。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什么是happens_before关系"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果一个操作的执行结果需要对另一个操作可见，那么这两个操作必须存在happens-before的关系。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"也就是说，在第二个操作执行的时候一都能够保证看到第一个操作执行的结果。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不具备happens_before的例子"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"pre","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-java"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"public class Visibility {\n    int x = 0;\n    public void write() {\n        x = 1;\n    }\n    public void read() {\n        int y = x;\n    }\n}\n"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果有两个线程，分别执行write和read方法，由于这两个线程没有相互配合的机制，所以write和read方法内的代码不具备happens_before关系, 其中的变量的可见性无法保证。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"假设线程 1 已经先执行了 write 方法，修改了共享变量 x 的值，然后线程 2 执行 read 方法去读取 x 的值，此时我们并不能确定线程 2 现在是否能读取到之前线程 1 对 x 所做的修改，线程 2 有可能看到这次修改，所以读到的 x 值是 1，也有可能看不到本次修改，所以读到的 x 值是最初始的 0。既然存在不确定性，那么 write 和 read 方法内的代码就不具备 happens-before 关系。相反，如果第一个操作 happens-before 第二个操作，那么第一个操作对于第二个操作而言一定是可见的。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"happens_before的规则有哪些"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"单线程规则"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在一个单独的线程中，按照代码的顺序，先执行的操作happens-before后执行的操作。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"单线程，无需考虑happens-before，反过来想，如果单线程的代码执行不能保证，岂不是乱套了。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://www.shiyitopo.tech/uPic/happens-before.png","alt":"happens-before"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意: 在单线程中，即使发生了指令重排，重排后的语义也必须符合happens-before的原则。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"锁操作规则"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"synchronized和lock接口。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果操作A是解锁，而操作B是对同一个锁的加锁，那么hb(A,B)"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://www.shiyitopo.tech/uPic/LockHappensBefor.png","alt":"LockHappensBefor"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"从上图中可以看到，有线程 A 和线程 B 这两个线程。线程 A 在解锁之前的所有操作，对于线程 B 的对同一个锁的加锁之后的所有操作而言，都是可见的。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"volatile变量规则"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对volatile变量的写操作happens-before后面对该变量的操作。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这就代表了呗volatile修饰的变量，每次修改之后，其他线程读取这个变量的时候，可以读取到这个变量的最新值。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"volatile可以保证可见性，就是由于这条规则规定的"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"线程启动规则"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Thread 对象的 start 方法 happen-before 此线程 run 方法中的每一个操作。如下图所示："}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://www.shiyitopo.tech/uPic/Cgq2xl57Dw6AdKyOAADBt-00qXo349.png","alt":"img"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在图中的例子中，左侧区域是线程 A 启动了一个子线程 B，而右侧区域是子线程 B，那么子线程 B 在执行 run 方法里面的语句的时候，它一定能看到父线程在执行 threadB.start() 前的所有操作的结果。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"线程join规则"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们知道 join 可以让线程之间等待，假设线程 A 通过调用 threadB.start() 启动了一个新线程 B，然后调用 threadB.join() ，那么线程 A 将一直等待到线程 B 的 run 方法结束（不考虑中断等特殊情况），然后 join 方法才返回。在 join 方法返回后，线程 A 中的所有后续操作都可以看到线程 B 的 run 方法中执行的所有操作的结果，也就是线程 B 的 run 方法里面的操作 happens-before 线程 A 的 join 之后的语句。如下图所示："},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://www.shiyitopo.tech/uPic/Cgq2xl57Dw6ADE7rAADRJKFrbWE816.png","alt":"img"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中断规则"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对线程的interrupt方法的调用happens-before检测该线程的中断事件。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"也就是说，如果一个线程被其他线程 interrupt，那么在检测中断时（比如调用 Thread.interrupted 或者 Thread.isInterrupted 方法）一定能看到此次中断的发生，不会发生检测结果不准的情况。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"并发工具类的规则"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"线程安全的并发容器（如 HashTable）在 get 某个值时一定能看到在此之前发生的 put 等存入操作的结果。也就是说，线程安全的并发容器的存入操作 happens-before 读取操作。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"信号量（Semaphore）它会释放许可证，也会获取许可证。这里的释放许可证的操作 happens-before 获取许可证的操作，也就是说，如果在获取许可证之前有释放许可证的操作，那么在获取时一定可以看到。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Future：Future 有一个 get 方法，可以用来获取任务的结果。那么，当 Future 的 get 方法得到结果的时候，一定可以看到之前任务中所有操作的结果，也就是说 Future 任务中的所有操作 happens-before Future 的 get 操作。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"线程池：要想利用线程池，就需要往里面提交任务（Runnable 或者 Callable），这里面也有一个 happens-before 关系的规则，那就是提交任务的操作 happens-before 任务的执行。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"总结"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"需要重点掌握的是，锁操作的happens-before和volatile的happens-before规则。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这两个规则与synchronized和volatile的使用有紧密的联系。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"除这两个之外的规则，可以不作为重点了解，这些规则都是被当做已知条件去使用的。"}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"headings":[{"depth":1,"value":"happens-before规则","slug":"happens-before规则"},{"depth":2,"value":"什么是happens_before关系","slug":"什么是happens_before关系"},{"depth":2,"value":"不具备happens_before的例子","slug":"不具备happens_before的例子"},{"depth":2,"value":"happens_before的规则有哪些","slug":"happens_before的规则有哪些"},{"depth":3,"value":"单线程规则","slug":"单线程规则"},{"depth":3,"value":"锁操作规则","slug":"锁操作规则"},{"depth":3,"value":"volatile变量规则","slug":"volatile变量规则"},{"depth":3,"value":"线程启动规则","slug":"线程启动规则"},{"depth":3,"value":"线程join规则","slug":"线程join规则"},{"depth":3,"value":"中断规则","slug":"中断规则"},{"depth":3,"value":"并发工具类的规则","slug":"并发工具类的规则"},{"depth":2,"value":"总结","slug":"总结-5"}]}},
